<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ru">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Анализ пары · {{ data.person_a.user.name }} & {{ data.person_b.user.name }}</title>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Cormorant+Garamond:ital,wght@0,300;0,400;0,500;1,300;1,400&family=Jost:wght@300;400;500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
*, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
:root {
  --black: #111110;
  --g900: #2C2C2A;
  --g700: #5F5E5A;
  --g500: #888780;
  --g300: #D3D1C7;
  --g100: #F1EFE8;
  --white: #FAFAF8;
  --rose: #C9A89A;
  --border: rgba(0,0,0,0.09);
  --border-md: rgba(0,0,0,0.15);
  --r-sm: 8px;
  --r-md: 12px;
  --r-lg: 16px;
}
html { font-size: 16px; scroll-behavior: smooth; }
body { font-family: 'Jost', sans-serif; font-weight: 300; background: var(--white); color: var(--g900); line-height: 1.6; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; }

/* COVER */
.cover { min-height: 100vh; padding: 4rem; display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: space-between; border-bottom: 0.5px solid var(--border); }
.cover-meta { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; font-size: 11px; letter-spacing: 0.12em; color: var(--g500); }
.cover-center { text-align: center; padding: 4rem 0 3rem; }
.cover-eyebrow { font-size: 11px; letter-spacing: 0.3em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--g500); margin-bottom: 1.5rem; }
.cover-title { font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif; font-size: clamp(48px, 8vw, 88px); font-weight: 300; line-height: 1.05; letter-spacing: -0.01em; color: var(--black); }
.cover-amp { display: inline-block; margin: 0 0.4rem; font-style: italic; color: var(--g500); }
.cover-sub { font-size: 12px; letter-spacing: 0.18em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--g500); margin-top: 1.5rem; }
.cover-pair-info { display: flex; justify-content: center; gap: 4rem; margin-top: 3rem; padding-top: 3rem; border-top: 0.5px solid var(--border); }
.pair-person { text-align: center; }
.pair-person .label { font-size: 10px; letter-spacing: 0.2em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--g500); margin-bottom: 0.4rem; }
.pair-person .name { font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif; font-size: 28px; font-weight: 300; color: var(--black); margin-bottom: 0.3rem; }
.pair-person .meta { font-size: 11px; color: var(--g700); letter-spacing: 0.05em; }
.cover-toc { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: flex-end; font-size: 10px; color: var(--g500); letter-spacing: 0.12em; text-transform: uppercase; margin-top: 3rem; }
.toc-items { display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 1rem 1.75rem; }

/* CHAPTER */
.chapter-divider { padding: 3rem 4rem 1.5rem; border-top: 0.5px solid var(--border); position: relative; overflow: hidden; }
.chap-eyebrow { font-size: 10px; letter-spacing: 0.25em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--g500); margin-bottom: 0.4rem; }
.chap-title-big { font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif; font-size: clamp(34px, 5vw, 52px); font-weight: 300; color: var(--black); letter-spacing: 0.01em; }
.chap-num { font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif; font-size: 120px; font-weight: 300; color: var(--g100); line-height: 1; position: absolute; right: 4rem; top: 50%; transform: translateY(-50%); pointer-events: none; }

/* PAGE */
.page { max-width: 920px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 3rem 4rem 4rem; }

/* CARDS */
.card { background: #fff; border: 0.5px solid var(--border); border-radius: var(--r-lg); padding: 1.4rem 1.75rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
.card-lbl { font-size: 10px; letter-spacing: 0.2em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--g500); margin-bottom: 1rem; padding-bottom: 0.7rem; border-bottom: 0.5px solid var(--border); }
.g2 { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 0.9rem; margin-bottom: 0.9rem; }
.g3 { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3,1fr); gap: 0.75rem; margin-bottom: 0.9rem; }
.mc { background: var(--g100); border-radius: var(--r-sm); padding: 0.95rem 1.05rem; }
.ml { font-size: 10px; letter-spacing: 0.13em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--g500); margin-bottom: 0.4rem; }
.mv { font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif; font-size: 20px; font-weight: 400; color: var(--black); margin-bottom: 0.3rem; }
.md { font-size: 12px; color: var(--g700); line-height: 1.55; }

/* COMPATIBILITY HEADER */
.compat-header { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 2rem; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; padding: 1.5rem 0; border-bottom: 0.5px solid var(--border); }
.compat-score-block { text-align: center; }
.compat-score { font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif; font-size: 64px; font-weight: 300; line-height: 1; color: var(--black); }
.compat-denom { font-size: 18px; color: var(--g500); }
.compat-info { flex: 1; }
.compat-type { font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif; font-size: 24px; font-weight: 400; color: var(--black); margin-bottom: 0.4rem; }
.compat-pair { font-size: 11px; letter-spacing: 0.15em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--g500); }

/* TEXT */
.q { font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif; font-style: italic; font-size: 17px; color: var(--g700); line-height: 1.65; margin-bottom: 1.1rem; padding-left: 1.1rem; border-left: 1px solid var(--g300); }
.bt { font-size: 13px; color: var(--g700); line-height: 1.7; }
.ri { display: flex; gap: 0.65rem; margin-bottom: 0.6rem; align-items: flex-start; }
.d { width: 4px; height: 4px; border-radius: 50%; background: var(--g500); margin-top: 7px; flex-shrink: 0; }
.dh { width: 4px; height: 4px; border-radius: 50%; border: 1px solid var(--g500); margin-top: 7px; flex-shrink: 0; }
.hl { color: var(--black); font-weight: 400; }

/* PERSON CARDS */
.person-card { background: var(--g100); border-radius: var(--r-sm); padding: 1.1rem 1.2rem; }
.person-name-mini { font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif; font-size: 18px; color: var(--black); margin-bottom: 0.4rem; font-weight: 400; }

/* RISK LEVEL */
.risk-pill { display: inline-block; font-size: 10px; letter-spacing: 0.12em; text-transform: uppercase; padding: 3px 11px; border-radius: 20px; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; font-weight: 400; }
.risk-low { background: rgba(80,150,80,0.12); color: #4a7a4a; }
.risk-medium { background: rgba(200,150,60,0.15); color: #8a6020; }
.risk-high { background: rgba(180,80,80,0.15); color: #8a3030; }

/* YEAR ROW */
.yr { display: flex; gap: 1.25rem; align-items: flex-start; padding: 1rem 0; border-bottom: 0.5px solid var(--border); }
.yr:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
.yr-period { font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif; font-size: 18px; font-weight: 400; color: var(--black); min-width: 120px; line-height: 1.2; }
.yr-phase { font-size: 11px; color: var(--g500); letter-spacing: 0.1em; text-transform: uppercase; margin-top: 4px; }
.yr-title { font-size: 13px; font-weight: 400; color: var(--black); margin-bottom: 0.3rem; }
.yr-desc { font-size: 12px; color: var(--g700); line-height: 1.55; }

/* DARK CARD */
.dark-card { background: var(--black); color: var(--white); border-radius: var(--r-lg); padding: 2rem 2.25rem; margin-bottom: 0.9rem; }
.dark-card .q { color: rgba(255,255,255,0.65); border-left-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.18); }
.dark-card .bt { color: rgba(255,255,255,0.6); }
.dark-card .hl { color: #fff; }
.dark-card .d { background: rgba(255,255,255,0.35); }
.dark-card .card-lbl { color: rgba(255,255,255,0.4); border-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.12); }

/* FINAL LINE */
.final-line { font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif; font-size: 18px; font-weight: 300; font-style: italic; color: var(--black); line-height: 1.6; margin-top: 1rem; padding: 1rem 1.25rem; border: 0.5px solid var(--border-md); border-radius: var(--r-md); }
.dark-card .final-line { border-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.14); color: rgba(255,255,255,0.85); }

/* HR */
hr { border: none; border-top: 0.5px solid var(--border); margin: 1.75rem 0; }

/* FOOTER */
.footer { text-align: center; padding: 3rem 4rem; border-top: 0.5px solid var(--border); font-size: 11px; color: var(--g500); letter-spacing: 0.07em; line-height: 2.2; }

/* LOCKED */
.locked-wrap { position: relative; margin-bottom: 1rem; border-radius: var(--r-lg); overflow: hidden; isolation: isolate; }
.locked-content { filter: blur(2px) saturate(0.95); pointer-events: none; user-select: none; opacity: 0.95; }
.locked-overlay { position: absolute; inset: 0; display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center; justify-content: center; gap: 0.85rem; padding: 1.5rem; background: radial-gradient(ellipse at center, rgba(250,250,248,0.45) 0%, rgba(250,250,248,0.78) 70%, rgba(250,250,248,0.92) 100%); text-align: center; }
.locked-icon { width: 46px; height: 46px; border-radius: 50%; background: var(--black); display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; box-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(0,0,0,0.18), 0 0 0 6px rgba(201,168,154,0.15); }
.locked-icon svg { width: 20px; height: 20px; stroke: var(--rose); fill: none; stroke-width: 1.6; }
.locked-eyebrow { font-size: 9.5px; letter-spacing: 0.28em; text-transform: uppercase; color: #8a6055; font-variant: small-caps; }
.locked-title { font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif; font-size: 22px; font-weight: 400; color: var(--black); line-height: 1.15; max-width: 26ch; }
.locked-pkg-name { font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif; font-style: italic; font-size: 14px; color: #8a6055; letter-spacing: 0.04em; margin-top: 2px; }

@media print {
  .cover { page-break-after: always; min-height: auto; }
  .page { page-break-inside: avoid; }
}

@media (max-width: 680px) {
  .cover { padding: 2.5rem 1.5rem; }
  .cover-pair-info { flex-direction: column; gap: 1.5rem; }
  .page { padding: 2rem 1.5rem 3rem; }
  .chapter-divider { padding: 2rem 1.5rem 1rem; }
  .g2, .g3 { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  .cover-toc { flex-direction: column; gap: 1rem; }
  .chap-num { display: none; }
  .compat-header { flex-direction: column; gap: 1rem; align-items: flex-start; }
  .yr { flex-direction: column; gap: 0.4rem; }
  .yr-period { min-width: 0; }
  .locked-title { font-size: 18px; }
  .locked-icon { width: 40px; height: 40px; }
}
</style>
</head>
<body>
{#- ══ ПЛАН ДОСТУПА ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════
    demo     — I, II (совместимость + хиромантия)
    base     — + III, V (верность + карма)
    extended — + IV, VI, VII (брак + богатство + дети)
    full     — + VIII, IX (длительность + точка разрыва)
══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ -#}
{%- set _plan_levels = {'demo': 0, 'base': 1, 'extended': 2, 'full': 3} -%}
{%- set _cur_level   = _plan_levels.get(plan | default('full'), 3) -%}
{%- set locked_cfg = {
  'compatibility':        {'min_plan': 'demo', 'title': 'Анализ совместимости',      'pkg': ''},
  'palmistry_heart':      {'min_plan': 'demo', 'title': 'Хиромантия пары',           'pkg': ''},
  'fidelity':             {'min_plan': 'base',     'title': 'Верность в паре',       'pkg': 'Базовый'},
  'karma':                {'min_plan': 'base',     'title': 'Карма в отношениях',    'pkg': 'Базовый'},
  'marriage_perspective': {'min_plan': 'extended', 'title': 'Перспектива брака',     'pkg': 'Расширенный'},
  'wealth':               {'min_plan': 'extended', 'title': 'Уровень богатства',     'pkg': 'Расширенный'},
  'family':               {'min_plan': 'extended', 'title': 'Семья и родительство', 'pkg': 'Расширенный'},
  'duration':             {'min_plan': 'full',     'title': 'Длительность союза',    'pkg': 'Премиум'},
  'breaking_point':       {'min_plan': 'full',     'title': 'Точка разрыва',         'pkg': 'Премиум'},
} -%}
{%- macro locked_card(min_plan, title, pkg) -%}
  {%- set min_level = _plan_levels.get(min_plan, 1) -%}
  {%- if _cur_level >= min_level -%}
{{ caller() }}
  {%- elif plan == 'demo' -%}
<div class="locked-wrap" aria-label="Заблокированный раздел">
  <div class="locked-content" aria-hidden="true">{{ caller() }}</div>
  <div class="locked-overlay">
    <div class="locked-icon" aria-hidden="true">
      <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><rect x="5" y="11" width="14" height="9" rx="2"></rect><path d="M8 11V7.5a4 4 0 0 1 8 0V11"></path><circle cx="12" cy="15.5" r="1.1" fill="currentColor" stroke="none" style="fill: var(--rose);"></circle></svg>
    </div>
    <div class="locked-eyebrow">Доступно в пакете</div>
    <div class="locked-title">{{ title }}</div>
    <div class="locked-pkg-name">{{ pkg }}</div>
  </div>
</div>
  {%- endif -%}
{%- endmacro -%}

<!-- COVER -->
<div class="cover">
  <div class="cover-meta">
    <span>Анализ совместимости пары</span>
    <span>Конфиденциально</span>
  </div>
  <div class="cover-center">
    <div class="cover-eyebrow">Глубинный портрет союза</div>
    <div class="cover-title">{{ data.person_a.user.name }}<span class="cover-amp">&amp;</span>{{ data.person_b.user.name }}</div>
    <div class="cover-sub">Совместимость · Хиромантия · Карма · Перспектива брака</div>

    <div class="cover-pair-info">
      <div class="pair-person">
        <div class="label">Партнёр A</div>
        <div class="name">{{ data.person_a.user.name }}</div>
        <div class="meta">{{ data.person_a.user.birthdate }} · {{ data.person_a.user.age }} лет<br>Число пути {{ data.person_a.numerology.life_path }} · {{ data.person_a.numerology.life_path_archetype.name }}</div>
      </div>
      <div class="pair-person">
        <div class="label">Партнёр Б</div>
        <div class="name">{{ data.person_b.user.name }}</div>
        <div class="meta">{{ data.person_b.user.birthdate }} · {{ data.person_b.user.age }} лет<br>Число пути {{ data.person_b.numerology.life_path }} · {{ data.person_b.numerology.life_path_archetype.name }}</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="cover-toc">
    <div class="toc-items">
      <span>I · Совместимость</span>
      <span>II · Хиромантия</span>
      <span>III · Верность</span>
      <span>IV · Перспектива брака</span>
      <span>V · Карма</span>
      <span>VI · Богатство</span>
      <span>VII · Семья</span>
      <span>VIII · Длительность</span>
      <span>IX · Точка разрыва</span>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>


<!-- ═══ I: СОВМЕСТИМОСТЬ ═══ -->
<div class="chapter-divider">
  <div class="chap-eyebrow">Часть первая</div>
  <div class="chap-title-big">Полный анализ совместимости</div>
  <div class="chap-num">I</div>
</div>

<div class="page">
{% call locked_card(locked_cfg.compatibility.min_plan, locked_cfg.compatibility.title, locked_cfg.compatibility.pkg) %}
  <div class="card">
    <div class="compat-header">
      <div class="compat-score-block">
        <div class="compat-score">{{ blocks.compatibility.compatibility_score }}</div>
        <div class="compat-denom">/ 10</div>
      </div>
      <div class="compat-info">
        <div class="compat-type">{{ data.couple.compatibility.type | capitalize }}</div>
        <div class="compat-pair">Числа пути {{ data.couple.compatibility.life_path_pair[0] }} · {{ data.couple.compatibility.life_path_pair[1] }}</div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <p class="q">{{ blocks.compatibility.verdict_quote }}</p>
    <div class="bt">{{ blocks.compatibility.summary }}</div>
  </div>

  <div class="card">
    <div class="card-lbl">Резонанс матриц</div>
    <div class="bt">{{ blocks.compatibility.matrix_resonance }}</div>
    <div class="g3" style="margin-top:1rem;">
      <div class="mc">
        <div class="ml">Число союза</div>
        <div class="mv">{{ data.couple.union_number.number }}</div>
        <div class="md">{{ data.couple.union_number.meaning }}</div>
      </div>
      <div class="mc">
        <div class="ml">Разница лет</div>
        <div class="mv">{{ data.couple.age.diff_years }}</div>
        <div class="md">{{ data.couple.age.category | capitalize }}</div>
      </div>
      <div class="mc">
        <div class="ml">Синхронность фаз</div>
        <div class="mv">{{ data.couple.year_sync.level | capitalize }}</div>
        <div class="md">{{ data.couple.year_sync.desc }}</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="g2">
    <div class="card" style="margin-bottom:0;">
      <div class="card-lbl">Сильные стороны пары</div>
      <div class="bt">
        {% for item in blocks.compatibility.strengths %}
        <div class="ri"><div class="d"></div><span>{{ item }}</span></div>
        {% endfor %}
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="card" style="margin-bottom:0;">
      <div class="card-lbl">Точки напряжения</div>
      <div class="bt">
        {% for item in blocks.compatibility.weaknesses %}
        <div class="ri"><div class="dh"></div><span>{{ item }}</span></div>
        {% endfor %}
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
{% endcall %}
</div>


<!-- ═══ II: ХИРОМАНТИЯ ═══ -->
<div class="chapter-divider">
  <div class="chap-eyebrow">Часть вторая</div>
  <div class="chap-title-big">Хиромантия пары</div>
  <div class="chap-num">II</div>
</div>

<div class="page">
{% call locked_card(locked_cfg.palmistry_heart.min_plan, locked_cfg.palmistry_heart.title, locked_cfg.palmistry_heart.pkg) %}
  <div class="card">
    <div class="card-lbl">Линия сердца — как каждый любит</div>
    <p class="q">{{ blocks.palmistry_heart.intro_quote }}</p>
    <div class="g2" style="margin-top:1rem;">
      <div class="person-card">
        <div class="person-name-mini">{{ data.person_a.user.name }}</div>
        <div class="bt">{{ blocks.palmistry_heart.person_a_pattern }}</div>
      </div>
      <div class="person-card">
        <div class="person-name-mini">{{ data.person_b.user.name }}</div>
        <div class="bt">{{ blocks.palmistry_heart.person_b_pattern }}</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="card">
    <div class="card-lbl">Динамика сердец</div>
    <div class="bt">{{ blocks.palmistry_heart.match_dynamic }}</div>
  </div>
{% endcall %}
</div>


<!-- ═══ III: ВЕРНОСТЬ ═══ -->
<div class="chapter-divider">
  <div class="chap-eyebrow">Часть третья</div>
  <div class="chap-title-big">Верность в паре</div>
  <div class="chap-num">III</div>
</div>

<div class="page">
{% call locked_card(locked_cfg.fidelity.min_plan, locked_cfg.fidelity.title, locked_cfg.fidelity.pkg) %}
  <div class="card">
    <p class="q">{{ blocks.fidelity.intro_quote }}</p>
    <div class="g2" style="margin-top:1rem;">
      <div class="person-card">
        <div class="person-name-mini">{{ data.person_a.user.name }}</div>
        <span class="risk-pill risk-{{ blocks.fidelity.person_a_risk.level | replace('низкий', 'low') | replace('средний', 'medium') | replace('высокий', 'high') }}">Риск: {{ blocks.fidelity.person_a_risk.level }}</span>
        <div class="bt">{{ blocks.fidelity.person_a_risk.desc }}</div>
      </div>
      <div class="person-card">
        <div class="person-name-mini">{{ data.person_b.user.name }}</div>
        <span class="risk-pill risk-{{ blocks.fidelity.person_b_risk.level | replace('низкий', 'low') | replace('средний', 'medium') | replace('высокий', 'high') }}">Риск: {{ blocks.fidelity.person_b_risk.level }}</span>
        <div class="bt">{{ blocks.fidelity.person_b_risk.desc }}</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="g2">
    <div class="card" style="margin-bottom:0;">
      <div class="card-lbl">Ситуации-триггеры</div>
      <div class="bt">
        {% for item in blocks.fidelity.trigger_situations %}
        <div class="ri"><div class="dh"></div><span>{{ item }}</span></div>
        {% endfor %}
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="card" style="margin-bottom:0;">
      <div class="card-lbl">Стабилизирующие факторы</div>
      <div class="bt">
        {% for item in blocks.fidelity.stabilizing_factors %}
        <div class="ri"><div class="d"></div><span>{{ item }}</span></div>
        {% endfor %}
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
{% endcall %}
</div>


<!-- ═══ IV: ПЕРСПЕКТИВА БРАКА ═══ -->
<div class="chapter-divider">
  <div class="chap-eyebrow">Часть четвёртая</div>
  <div class="chap-title-big">Перспектива брака по годам</div>
  <div class="chap-num">IV</div>
</div>

<div class="page">
{% call locked_card(locked_cfg.marriage_perspective.min_plan, locked_cfg.marriage_perspective.title, locked_cfg.marriage_perspective.pkg) %}
  <p class="q" style="margin-bottom:1.5rem;">{{ blocks.marriage_perspective.intro_quote }}</p>

  <div class="card">
    {% for y in blocks.marriage_perspective.years %}
    <div class="yr">
      <div>
        <div class="yr-period">{{ y.year_range }}</div>
        <div class="yr-phase">{{ y.phase }}</div>
      </div>
      <div style="flex:1;">
        <div class="yr-desc">{{ y.desc }}</div>
      </div>
    </div>
    {% endfor %}
  </div>
{% endcall %}
</div>


<!-- ═══ V: КАРМА ═══ -->
<div class="chapter-divider">
  <div class="chap-eyebrow">Часть пятая</div>
  <div class="chap-title-big">Карма в отношениях</div>
  <div class="chap-num">V</div>
</div>

<div class="page">
{% call locked_card(locked_cfg.karma.min_plan, locked_cfg.karma.title, locked_cfg.karma.pkg) %}
  <div class="card">
    <p class="q">{{ blocks.karma.intro_quote }}</p>
    <div class="card-lbl" style="margin-top:1rem;">Урок для пары</div>
    <div class="bt">{{ blocks.karma.lesson_for_pair }}</div>
  </div>

  <div class="g2">
    <div class="person-card">
      <div class="person-name-mini">{{ data.person_a.user.name }}</div>
      <div class="ml">Личный урок</div>
      <div class="bt">{{ blocks.karma.lesson_a }}</div>
    </div>
    <div class="person-card">
      <div class="person-name-mini">{{ data.person_b.user.name }}</div>
      <div class="ml">Личный урок</div>
      <div class="bt">{{ blocks.karma.lesson_b }}</div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="final-line">{{ blocks.karma.final_line }}</div>
{% endcall %}
</div>


<!-- ═══ VI: БОГАТСТВО ═══ -->
<div class="chapter-divider">
  <div class="chap-eyebrow">Часть шестая</div>
  <div class="chap-title-big">Уровень богатства в семье</div>
  <div class="chap-num">VI</div>
</div>

<div class="page">
{% call locked_card(locked_cfg.wealth.min_plan, locked_cfg.wealth.title, locked_cfg.wealth.pkg) %}
  <div class="card">
    <p class="q">{{ blocks.wealth.intro_quote }}</p>
    <div style="text-align:center;padding:1.5rem 0 1rem;margin-bottom:1rem;border-bottom:0.5px solid var(--border);">
      <div class="ml" style="margin-bottom:0.5rem;">Уровень потенциала</div>
      <div style="font-family:'Cormorant Garamond',serif;font-size:30px;font-weight:300;color:var(--black);">{{ blocks.wealth.level | capitalize }}</div>
    </div>
    <div class="card-lbl">Денежный паттерн</div>
    <div class="bt" style="margin-bottom:1rem;">{{ blocks.wealth.money_pattern }}</div>
    <div class="bt">
      {% for item in blocks.wealth.points %}
      <div class="ri"><div class="d"></div><span>{{ item }}</span></div>
      {% endfor %}
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="card">
    <div class="card-lbl">Что блокирует благосостояние</div>
    <div class="bt">
      {% for item in blocks.wealth.blocking_factors %}
      <div class="ri"><div class="dh"></div><span>{{ item }}</span></div>
      {% endfor %}
    </div>
  </div>
{% endcall %}
</div>


<!-- ═══ VII: СЕМЬЯ ═══ -->
<div class="chapter-divider">
  <div class="chap-eyebrow">Часть седьмая</div>
  <div class="chap-title-big">Семья и родительство</div>
  <div class="chap-num">VII</div>
</div>

<div class="page">
{% call locked_card(locked_cfg.family.min_plan, locked_cfg.family.title, locked_cfg.family.pkg) %}
  <div class="card">
    <p class="q">{{ blocks.family.intro_quote }}</p>
    <div style="text-align:center;padding:1.5rem 0 1rem;margin-bottom:1rem;border-bottom:0.5px solid var(--border);">
      <div class="ml" style="margin-bottom:0.5rem;">Потенциал</div>
      <div style="font-family:'Cormorant Garamond',serif;font-size:30px;font-weight:300;color:var(--black);">{{ blocks.family.potential_level | capitalize }}</div>
    </div>
    <div class="bt">
      {% for item in blocks.family.points %}
      <div class="ri"><div class="d"></div><span>{{ item }}</span></div>
      {% endfor %}
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="card">
    <div class="card-lbl">Оптимальное время</div>
    <div class="bt">{{ blocks.family.timing }}</div>
  </div>
{% endcall %}
</div>


<!-- ═══ VIII: ДЛИТЕЛЬНОСТЬ ═══ -->
<div class="chapter-divider">
  <div class="chap-eyebrow">Часть восьмая</div>
  <div class="chap-title-big">Краткосрочная история или долгий союз</div>
  <div class="chap-num">VIII</div>
</div>

<div class="page">
{% call locked_card(locked_cfg.duration.min_plan, locked_cfg.duration.title, locked_cfg.duration.pkg) %}
  <div class="card">
    <p class="q">{{ blocks.duration.intro_quote }}</p>
    <div style="text-align:center;padding:1.5rem 0 1rem;margin-bottom:1rem;border-bottom:0.5px solid var(--border);">
      <div class="ml" style="margin-bottom:0.5rem;">Тип союза</div>
      <div style="font-family:'Cormorant Garamond',serif;font-size:24px;font-weight:300;color:var(--black);line-height:1.3;">{{ blocks.duration.type | capitalize }}</div>
    </div>
    <div class="bt">{{ blocks.duration.summary }}</div>
  </div>

  <div class="g2">
    <div class="card" style="margin-bottom:0;">
      <div class="card-lbl">Что удлинит союз</div>
      <div class="bt">
        {% for item in blocks.duration.factors_extending %}
        <div class="ri"><div class="d"></div><span>{{ item }}</span></div>
        {% endfor %}
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="card" style="margin-bottom:0;">
      <div class="card-lbl">Что укоротит</div>
      <div class="bt">
        {% for item in blocks.duration.factors_shortening %}
        <div class="ri"><div class="dh"></div><span>{{ item }}</span></div>
        {% endfor %}
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
{% endcall %}
</div>


<!-- ═══ IX: ТОЧКА РАЗРЫВА ═══ -->
<div class="chapter-divider">
  <div class="chap-eyebrow">Часть девятая</div>
  <div class="chap-title-big">Точка разрыва</div>
  <div class="chap-num">IX</div>
</div>

<div class="page">
{% call locked_card(locked_cfg.breaking_point.min_plan, locked_cfg.breaking_point.title, locked_cfg.breaking_point.pkg) %}
  <div class="dark-card">
    <div class="card-lbl">Если разрыв случится</div>
    <p class="q">{{ blocks.breaking_point.intro_quote }}</p>
    <div class="bt" style="margin-bottom:1rem;">
      <div class="ri"><div class="d"></div><span><span class="hl">Вероятность:</span> {{ blocks.breaking_point.probability }}</span></div>
      <div class="ri"><div class="d"></div><span><span class="hl">Триггер:</span> {{ blocks.breaking_point.trigger }}</span></div>
      <div class="ri"><div class="d"></div><span><span class="hl">Время:</span> {{ blocks.breaking_point.timing }}</span></div>
    </div>
    <div class="card-lbl">Что предотвратит</div>
    <div class="bt">
      {% for item in blocks.breaking_point.preventable_by %}
      <div class="ri"><div class="d"></div><span>{{ item }}</span></div>
      {% endfor %}
    </div>
    <div class="final-line">{{ blocks.breaking_point.final_line }}</div>
  </div>
{% endcall %}
</div>


<div class="footer">
  Анализ пары · {{ data.person_a.user.name }} ({{ data.person_a.user.birthdate }}) и {{ data.person_b.user.name }} ({{ data.person_b.user.birthdate }})<br>
  Совместимость · Хиромантия · Верность · Перспектива брака · Карма · Богатство · Семья · Длительность · Точка разрыва<br>
  Анализ носит интерпретационный характер. Эзотерика — язык символов, не детерминизм.
</div>

</body>
</html>
